snippet.title: Star Overdrive – Nintendo Direct: Partner Showcase 8.27.2024
snippet.description:
Star Overdrive is coming to Nintendo Switch in 2025! 

Speed into the unknown in Star Overdrive! Battle and explore a vast world where creativity is key to overcoming challenges. 

#StarOverdrive #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
